{"tid":2009744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去年伊拉克示威導致時任總理下台 新政府承諾釋放示威者","createTime":"2020-05-10T03:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T05:38:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"829fbdc43622565f829499ccc0f939286efa1b3b","tid":2009744,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕伊拉克新政府當地時間9日表示，將釋放去年10月大規模抗議活動被逮捕的示威者，承諾為示威者伸張正義，並將為死者家屬提供賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/10/php0tyiQR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F10%2Fphp0tyiQR.jpg&h=2337de97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，伊拉克新任總理哈德米（Mustafa Kadhemi）首次內閣會議後宣布，因參與10月抗議活動被逮捕的人都將被釋放，哈德米也誓言，將為所有流血的伊拉克人追究責任。<br />\n<br />\n伊拉克在去年10月爆發大規模的示威活動，示威者因失業、政府腐敗以及鄰國伊朗對國內事務的影響等議題發起抗議活動，民眾走上街頭要求政府改革，軍警鎮壓導致數百人喪生。<br />\n<br />\n前總理馬蒂（Adel Abdel Mahdi）政府多次表示，無法找出向示威者開火的槍手，哈德米政府則宣布，將成立委員會，調查10月至今針對示威者的襲擊。哈德米也承諾，將與示威者進行協商。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，伊拉克去年10月爆發的反政府示威，多次的血腥鎮壓導致超過550人死亡，上萬人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3160714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3160714&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=7ecaa7d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3160714&h=974ccd29\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3160714</a>"},{"pid":"d37fbaee29c77294f9e4f25128732e2da2d89f19","tid":2009744,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"香港可借鑑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=418ad61d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_Wq9lQZA_Xc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_Wq9lQZA_Xc&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=dbdaefc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_Wq9lQZA_Xc</a>"},{"pid":"de3f9abfd6037179279d3cedfb222de4612a6826","tid":2009744,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:50:49.000Z","msg":"陷家剷<br />\n伊拉克都有委員會<br />\n我地就連個監警小學雞報告都唔敢出"},{"pid":"e7c08c7a19c386137a22d920072c898203181e81","tid":2009744,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9118fe863137b9d92772ae4dbd9ddbeae66cb0","tid":2009744,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9b1293aeb7c6b1a8fa243295da9dc82b8ca437","tid":2009744,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bb237cd7bd49f105a43ba754a77dd0e1b3fd285","tid":2009744,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb9b1293aeb7c6b1a8fa243295da9dc82b8ca437","tid":2009744,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"上一手總理好似係自己辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d7c519b05e165dc1820f7a2c48e94c04ba58a8","tid":2009744,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"好多人忽略左伊拉克和平同穩定左之後GDP 十幾個